              <p>The August 2022 consultation on Digitalisation of Business Rates (DBR). <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/digitalising-business-rates-connecting-business-rates-and-tax-data"><u>https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/digitalising-business-rates-connecting-business-rates-and-tax-data</u></a></p>
            </content>
