      <section eId="section_9">
        <heading><b>Annex B - Hansard References</b></heading>
        <paragraph>
          <num>89 </num>
          <content>
            <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act's passage through Parliament.</p>
            <table ukm:widths="1.75in 1.48in 3.22in">
              <tr>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Hansard Reference</b></p>
                </th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p>House of Commons</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>29 March 2023</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p />
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>24 April 2023</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2023-04-24/debates/7703DDEE-E034-4863-813E-CB28C7105E29/Non-DomesticRatingBill"><u>Vol. 731 Col. 529</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Committee of the Whole House</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>22 May 2023</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2023-05-22/debates/0361F456-F366-45A6-A7A3-EAD90F40F926/Non-DomesticRatingBill"><u>Vol. 733 Col. 55</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Third Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>22 May 2023</p>
                </td>
